org.apache.poi.hwpf.model

Class SavedByTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwpf.model.SavedByTable

  • @Internal
public final class SavedByTable
extends java.lang.Object
    String table containing the history of the last few revisions ("saves") of the document. Read-only for the time being.(包含文档最后几个修订（“保存”）历史的字符串表。暂时只读。)
    Author:
    Daniel Noll
